10
00:01:11,353 --> 00:01:15,565
<i>DMA M1, M2, M3 dan M4 selesai.</i>

11
00:01:15,607 --> 00:01:18,275
<i>Baiklah. Pesan diterima, Explorer.</i>

12
00:01:18,734 --> 00:01:20,652
